text: FOURTH: I have previously entered into a Revocable Trust Agreement (Inter Vivos Trust) with [Organization-1] at Twin Falls, Idaho. It is intended that almost all of my property will be controlled by that instrument and this Will shall simply operate to dispose of those few items not in the trust and otherwise to pour the rest, residue and remainder of my estate over into the Trust.

texts: those few items not in the trust
the rest, residue and remainder of my estate
